Jadi Pete tidak curiga.

513
00:44:37,500 --> 00:44:39,540
Hei, kamu mau kemana?

514
00:45:42,660 --> 00:45:43,980
Jack, Jack, tunggu sebentar.

515
00:45:45,100 --> 00:45:46,100
Biarkan aku menarik napas.

516
00:45:46,540 --> 00:45:47,540
saya lelah.

